{"tid":2309763,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【求中文大師解答】咩中文黎架？","createTime":"2020-12-02T19:03:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-02T19:48:30.000Z","uid":137277,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a9ca3f20e01e3621d9536b354321efa72ee5669c","tid":2309763,"uid":137277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T19:03:33.000Z","msg":"話說喺立場見到有篇文，有無人睇得明呢段野。。。<br />\n<br />\n雲淡輕吹，晴空廣闊，笛響起航，浪花湧濺，啞鈴外型，漁船避風，北眺亭望，樓房密集，張保仔洞，尋寶探秘，風帆花園，印記歷史，橫街窄巷，單車穿梭，坊里碰面，駐足傾談，黃昏夕照，漫步東灣，縷縷幽香，帶路指引，灰牆拉閘，樹幹檯櫈，音樂悠揚，步伐放緩，一杯咖啡，暫忘煩憂。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/personal/小島咖啡-聚友歡樂/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpersonal%2F%E5%B0%8F%E5%B3%B6%E5%92%96%E5%95%A1-%E8%81%9A%E5%8F%8B%E6%AD%A1%E6%A8%82%2F&d=u42ujRIT%2FE%2FeodHrCKN%2BOYaGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=7e2112f0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpersonal%2F%E5%B0%8F%E5%B3%B6%E5%92%96%E5%95%A1-%E8%81%9A%E5%8F%8B%E6%AD%A1%E6%A8%82%2F&h=8f321493\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/personal/小島咖啡-聚友歡樂/</a><br />\n<br />\n究竟咩係啞鈴外型？有無人話到俾我知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3acb4f7e1279c349b137e015fd7f7e606f20d3f6","tid":2309763,"uid":167177,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T19:06:06.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母，戇撚鳩鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42e1d5a289660bb59e9a69fd414304b9cb2ac52a","tid":2309763,"uid":357031,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T19:07:04.000Z","msg":"啞鈴外型都唔知邊度？篇文入面都有講啦，巴打你好打有限喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"034cae952b08355c6c9250b7dd0238a46382a120","tid":2309763,"uid":39019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T19:07:38.000Z","msg":"可能講緊長期嘅形狀<br />\n<br />\n「長洲位於大嶼山東南方，島上人口約3萬，是離島區中人煙最稠密的島嶼。<br />\n<br />\n長洲之名，最早見於明朝萬歷年間編的《粵大記》，因島形狹長，且兩頭大、中間細，因而得名。根據清朝嘉慶廿四年（1819年）編的《新安縣志》載：「長洲：在急水門外，大奚山南，長十餘里，商賈多聚於此。」另外，亦有人覺得它像一個啞鈴而稱它為啞鈴島（Dumbbell Island)。」"},{"pid":"95d42634460b48ebaaa67d9bbb37e4b546ae4bd7","tid":2309763,"uid":39019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T19:08:39.000Z","msg":"可能講緊長洲嘅形狀<br />\n<br />\n「長洲位於大嶼山東南方，島上人口約3萬，是離島區中人煙最稠密的島嶼。<br />\n<br />\n長洲之名，最早見於明朝萬歷年間編的《粵大記》，因島形狹長，且兩頭大、中間細，因而得名。根據清朝嘉慶廿四年（1819年）編的《新安縣志》載：「長洲：在急水門外，大奚山南，長十餘里，商賈多聚於此。」另外，亦有人覺得它像一個啞鈴而稱它為啞鈴島（Dumbbell Island)。」"},{"pid":"2e2c3db45c7014c8ee112b170cbd3bff53deaaf3","tid":2309763,"uid":137277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42e1d5a289660bb59e9a69fd414304b9cb2ac52a","tid":2309763,"uid":357031,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T19:07:04.000Z","msg":"啞鈴外型都唔知邊度？篇文入面都有講啦，巴打你好打有限喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T19:09:24.000Z","msg":"你叻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我睇唔明篇文<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3679c829f75dfe89a4e1c9edd66b822573c8fa0e","tid":2309763,"uid":137277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T19:10:50.000Z","msg":"啞鈴西南<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真心唔知作者噏乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n啞鈴西南，船廿分鐘，遙望城樓，匾刻康復，登踏山徑，舒適寧靜，島北大石，中央低陷，渾圓平放，故稱石鼓，航途逝世，立碑念妻，漁民傳訛，洲名棺材，歷史陳蹟，遺址印證，數步之距，見魯班廟，參觀音廟，察天后廟，心靈廣場，白玉佛像，細緻雕琢，洗滌放空，聖家小堂，室雅禱告，戴妃兩臨，築樓記事，屋舍散怖，打理潔淨，院友分工，齊心協力，遠離迷惑，忘記昨天<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/personal/%E5%B0%8F%E5%B3%B6%E6%88%92%E6%AF%92-%E5%BA%B7%E5%BE%A9%E8%A6%93%E8%B7%AF/?fbclid=IwAR2tumqp0hrgQSFNISSD8sjJhMZGSxjukYWcR-R3ztu5GS4ZNHHplcKnamk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpersonal%2F%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%25B3%